OL,5, The technology behind smart motorway   
OL,6, systems did not work for 21 hours      
OL,7, during September the BBC can reveal.   
OL,9,FCameras and radar alert a control room 
OL,10,Fto vehicles which have stopped in live 
OL,11,Flanes with overhead signs then being   
OL,12,Fused to tell drivers about issues.     
OL,14,FHowever, new data shows the system was 
OL,15,Fnot functioning for 3% of operational  
OL,16,Fhours in September, with an outage in  
OL,17,FOctober lasting nearly 4 hours.        
OL,19,FNational Highways said an independent  
OL,20,Finvestigation was under way.           
